/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 56 542.0 Tm (A fulgurite is a fossil of an instant. The passage of a lightning current through sand heats) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 528.0 Tm (a narrow channel beyond the melting point of quartz, and the sand fuses into a hollow glass) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 514.0 Tm (tube that freezes the discharge path in place. Few geological features form so fast or) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 500.0 Tm (record so singular an event.) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 486.0 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 56 472.0 Tm (This study excavated and reconstructed forty fulgurites from a single dune field to ask what) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 458.0 Tm (controls their shape and how briefly they form. Because each fulgurite traces one discharge,) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 444.0 Tm (the population offers a rare library of individual lightning paths through the subsurface.) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 430.0 Tm () Tj
