/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 56 398.0 Tm (Fulgurites are fragile and typically shatter if pulled from the ground carelessly. We) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 384.0 Tm (exposed each specimen by careful removal of surrounding sand, documented its) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 370.0 Tm (three-dimensional form in place, and lifted it in consolidated sections for reassembly in) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 356.0 Tm (the laboratory.) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 342.0 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 56 328.0 Tm (Reconstruction allowed us to measure total length, branching pattern, tube diameter, and) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 314.0 Tm (wall thickness, and to relate these to the grain size and inferred moisture of the sand at) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 300.0 Tm (each depth. The host sand, sampled alongside, provided the context the glass alone could) Tj
