1 0 0 1 56 708.0 Tm (testifies to how little time heat had to spread outward from the channel.) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 694.0 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 56 680.0 Tm (This brevity is what makes fulgurites such clean recorders. There is no slow cooling to blur) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 666.0 Tm (the structure, no later reworking of a feature buried in an instant. The fulgurite captures) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 652.0 Tm (one discharge and nothing else, which is precisely what makes its morphology so legible.) Tj
